{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-awesome-all-timeline-js","path":"/2018/04/04/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Track Awesome List"}},"allAwesomeItem":{"nodes":[{"awesomeListRepo":"hangtwenty/dive-into-machine-learning","categoryHTML":"<h2>Finding Open-Source Libraries</h2>","itemHTML":"<li><a href=\"https://www.tensorflow.org/\">TensorFlow</a> has been a <a href=\"https://news.ycombinator.com/item?id=10532957\">really big deal.</a> People like you will do exciting things with TensorFlow. It's a framework. Frameworks can help you manage complexity. Just remember this rule of thumb: <strong>\"More data beats a cleverer algorithm\"</strong> (Domingos), no matter how cool your tools are. Also note, TensorFlow is not the only machine learning framework of its kind: <strong><a href=\"https://github.com/zer0n/deepframeworks\">Check this great, detailed comparison of TensorFlow, Torch, and Theano.</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/zer0n/deepframeworks\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">2.1k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":2067,\"repo\":\"zer0n/deepframeworks\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--></strong> See also <a href=\"https://github.com/Newmu/Theano-Tutorials\">Newmu/Theano-Tutorials</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/Newmu/Theano-Tutorials\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.2k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1230,\"repo\":\"Newmu/Theano-Tutorials\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> and  <a href=\"https://github.com/nlintz/TensorFlow-Tutorials\">nlintz/TensorFlow-Tutorials</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nlintz/TensorFlow-Tutorials\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">5.9k</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":5906,\"repo\":\"nlintz/TensorFlow-Tutorials\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END-->. See also the section on Deep Learning above.\n<ul>\n<li>Also, consider <a href=\"https://github.com/instacart/lore/\">Lore</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/instacart/lore/\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.5k</span></spa